title: error: redefinition of ‘struct THSByteTensor
body_html: Hi, When I compile source code, I get a error "/restools/tools/anaconda2/include/THS/THSTensor.h:7:40: error: redefinition of ‘struct THSByteTensor’" . The compiling command I used is "sudo python setup.py install ". How should I resolve it?
